article_title: Obamacare's Sixth Birthday Provides No Reason To Celebrate

article_metadata.description: This week, Obamacare turns six years old. But while the president gears up to celebrate, Americans should make a birthday wish of their own -- to replace Obamacare with a plan that actually works.
article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes
